Hybrid code search (dense + lexical + reranker), ReFRAG micro-chunking, local LLM prompt enhancement, and dual SSE/RMCP endpoints. One command deploys Qdrant-powered indexing for Cursor, Windsurf, Roo, Cline, Codex, and any MCP client.
